Casablanca,t2jBSAWCg5s,Ugzhk2-O0Y3uiUGIg8h4AaABAg,,@thomastimlin1724,"Yvonne was played by French refugee  actress Madeline Lebeau, who was only 18/19 years old when they filmed this in1942. Her husband is actor Marcel Dalio, who played Emil the croupier [roulette wheel operator and general manager of the  gambling. room.. In June 1940, Lebeau and Dalio (who was Jewish) fled Paris ahead of the invading German Army and reached Lisbon. Sounds familiar doesn't it? They divorced shortly after the  film was made. Lebeau has the  honor of being the last surviving cast member of  Casablanca. Born on 10 June 1923, died 1 May 2016 (aged 92).",2026-05-02T21:02:23Z,2026-05-02T21:02:23Z,1,False,0.0,2026-05-07T02:01:21.481910
