Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyIVqczQ0iOrKhcO6l4AaABAg,,@jpdavies6278,"Le Jardin Majorelle/YSL and Berber museum are wonderful - went the day after seeing Le Secret Jardin (their gift shop is amazing don't miss local artizens who work & sell there)  near the Riad we were staying at.  Highly recommend Medina Sky for dinner a very special place with amazing service and lastly go to the Atlas Mountains specifically  go to women's Collective Dar Zite - the best Argon Oil and mountain rose perfume.  Only hint while walking in Medina stay by the walls when the scooters go by.  They will run you over. Local and tourist alike. 
