Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAg6gLrMqW1,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@dotted8-,"@FindingGinaMarie But you could go visit the replica, Rick’s American Cafe in Casablanca.",2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,2024-11-11T01:26:49Z,0,True,,2026-05-07T02:02:08.787055
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg.AAWZ6K3mxNBAAhYRSiFUYB,Ugw7a45JQ1LH6NfVopV4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"It's surprisingly less kitchy than I would have expected, but we prefer to not move around too much, so being in two cities and a three-day Sahara Desert tour was plenty for us! I don't know that the rest of Casablanca would have lived up to the hype of the movie. —Judy",2024-11-11T14:48:33Z,2024-11-11T14:48:33Z,0,True,,2026-05-07T02:02:08.787059
