Tourism,wFZyNQAIcdE,UgxfVvXc7JqTlvFYxg54AaABAg,,@japrindo,"As an indonesian, I am partial to Bali. Not sure why it's on the list and I dont feel that it's fair to mention the entire island is a regrettable place to visit. Perhaps like what video indicated maybe some areas of the island like Seminyak or Kuta - I agree - they are not the most ideal place due to trash/cleanliness issues, traffic and crowds. However Bali has so much more to offer - there are other areas like Ubud, Sanur or northeast Bali which are still quite a worthwhile place to visit!",2026-05-06T05:56:26Z,2026-05-06T05:56:26Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-07T02:02:54.753807
