Tourism,wFZyNQAIcdE,UgxhDX-iPxZwX-QWx1F4AaABAg,,@MrBulky992,"It seems to me that a lot of these tourists go around the world with a checklist of iconic sights and have no interest in anything other than taking a selfie there and nothing else besides, no matter how close by and how interesting.  I have no doubt this is about being able to boast about ""being there"" to their acquaintances.  ""Pearls before swine"" comes to mind.  Apparently a gondola ride and the Rialto bridge are all there is to see and do in Venice!  Of course it helps to have had an education to appreciate everything else but what about the Doge's Palace, St Mark's Cathedral and Square and the many churches, palazzi and art galleries, the La Fenice opera house and nearby Murano to see glass-blowing?",2026-05-03T00:45:26Z,2026-05-03T00:46:37Z,0,False,0.0,2026-05-07T02:02:54.754049
